<br><br>
Unfortunately, the delay was generated because the bank decided to block the bank account which we processed all of the payment methods that we offer in Chile. By identifying this problem, we worked hard to find a reasonable explanation for this, as well as looked to other financial institutions to open collecting bank accounts in order to continue operating in Chile.
<br><br>
Currently, we are in this process, although we have noticed that financial institutions are resistant to provide banking services to companies that collect payments on the Internet for third parties, essentially representing the service that we will provide to our customers. We are working very hard and hope to resolve this situation in the coming days.=20
<br><br>
For the past 9 years, we have operated in Chile and during this time we have operated in the most transparent and professional way possible, characteristics that we not only promote in Chile, but also in all of the countries where we operate.=20
<br><br>
We are aware of the large impact that this situation has caused for your business. Therefore, we reiterate our apologies and we confirm that we are taking all necessary actions to ensure this situation does not arise in the future. We will keep you informed of our efforts.=20
<br><br>
Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have any comment or additional questions.=20
<br><br>

